(100103,2,'Awesome Java','Frameworks that ease bean mapping. Tools that handle the build cycle and dependencies of an application. Libraries to manipulate bytecode programmatically. Libraries that provide caching facilities.','# Awesome Java\n\n> 这是Github上关于Java相关的工具，框架等等资源集合. 原文参考: https://github.com/akullpp/awesome-java。 @pdai\n\n- Awesome JavaBean MappingBuildBytecode ManipulationCachingCLICluster ManagementCode AnalysisCode CoverageCode GeneratorsCompiler-compilerConfigurationConstraint Satisfaction Problem SolverCSVDatabaseData StructuresDate and TimeDependency InjectionDevelopmentDistributed ApplicationsDistributed TransactionsDistributionDocument ProcessingFormal VerificationFunctional ProgrammingGame DevelopmentGeospatialGUIHigh PerformanceHTTP ClientsHypermedia TypesIDEImageryJSONJSON ProcessingJVM and JDKLoggingMachine LearningMessagingMiscellaneousMicroserviceMonitoringNativeNatural Language ProcessingNetworkingORMPaaSPDFPerformance analysisPlatformApache CommonsOtherProcessesReactive librariesREST FrameworksScienceSearchSecuritySerializationServerTemplate EngineTestingAsynchronousBDDFixturesFrameworksMatchersMiscellaneousMockingParameterizationUtilityVersion ManagersWeb CrawlingWeb Frameworks\n- ResourcesAwesome ListsCommunitiesFrontendsInfluential BooksPodcasts and ScreencastsTwitterWebsites\n- Contributing\n\n## Bean Mapping\n\n*Frameworks that ease bean mapping.*\n\n- [Dozer在新窗口打开](https://github.com/DozerMapper/dozer) - Mapper that copies data from one object to another using annotations and API or XML configuration.\n- [JMapper在新窗口打开](https://jmapper-framework.github.io/jmapper-core) - Uses byte code manipulation for lightning-fast mapping. Supports annotations and API or XML configuration.\n- [MapStruct在新窗口打开](https://github.com/mapstruct/mapstruct) - Code generator that simplifies mappings between different bean types, based on a convention-over-configuration approach.\n- [ModelMapper在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jhalterman/modelmapper) - Intelligent object mapping library that automatically maps objects to each other.\n- [Orika在新窗口打开](https://github.com/orika-mapper/orika) - JavaBean-mapping framework that recursively copies (among other capabilities) data from one object to another.\n- [Selma在新窗口打开](https://github.com/xebia-france/selma) - Annotation processor-based bean mapper.\n\n## Build\n\n*Tools that handle the build cycle and dependencies of an application.*\n\n- [Apache Maven在新窗口打开](https://maven.apache.org) - Declarative build and dependency management that favors convention over configuration. It might be preferable to Apache Ant, which uses a rather procedural approach and can be difficult to maintain.\n- [Bazel在新窗口打开](https://bazel.io) - Tool from Google that builds code quickly and reliably.\n- [Buck在新窗口打开](https://github.com/facebook/buck) - Encourages the creation of small, reusable modules consisting of code and resources.\n- [Gradle在新窗口打开](https://gradle.org) - Incremental builds programmed via Groovy instead of declaring XML. Works well with Maven\'s dependency management.\n\n## Bytecode Manipulation\n\n*Libraries to manipulate bytecode programmatically.*\n\n- [ASM在新窗口打开](http://asm.ow2.org) - All-purpose, low-level bytecode manipulation and analysis.\n- [Byte Buddy在新窗口打开](http://bytebuddy.net) - Further simplifies bytecode generation with a fluent API.\n- [bytecode-viewer在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Konloch/bytecode-viewer) - Java 8 Jar & Android APK reverse engineering suite.\n- [Byteman在新窗口打开](https://byteman.jboss.org) - Manipulate bytecode at runtime via DSL (rules); mainly for testing/troubleshooting.\n- [cglib在新窗口打开](https://github.com/cglib/cglib) - Bytecode generation library.\n- [Javassist在新窗口打开](https://jboss-javassist.github.io/javassist) - Tries to simplify bytecode editing.\n- [Mixin在新窗口打开](https://github.com/SpongePowered/Mixin) - Manipulate bytecode at runtime using real Java code.\n\n## Caching\n\n*Libraries that provide caching facilities.*\n\n- [Caffeine在新窗口打开](https://github.com/ben-manes/caffeine) - High-performance, near-optimal caching library.\n- [Ehcache在新窗口打开](http://www.ehcache.org) - Distributed general-purpose cache.\n- [Infinispan在新窗口打开](http://infinispan.org) - Highly concurrent key/value datastore used for caching.\n\n## CLI\n\n*Libraries for everything related to the CLI.*\n\n- [ASCII Table在新窗口打开](https://github.com/vdmeer/asciitable) - Library to draw tables in ASCII.\n- [Airline在新窗口打开](https://github.com/airlift/airline) - Annotation-based framework for parsing Git-like command-line arguments.\n- [args4j在新窗口打开](http://args4j.kohsuke.org) - Small library to parse command-line arguments.\n- [Jansi在新窗口打开](https://github.com/fusesource/jansi) - ANSI escape codes to format console output.\n- [Java ASCII Render在新窗口打开](https://github.com/indvd00m/java-ascii-render) - Graphical primitives for the console.\n- [JCommander在新窗口打开](http://jcommander.org) - Command-line argument-parsing framework with custom types and validation via implementing interfaces.\n- [JLine在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jline/jline3) - Includes features from modern shells like completion or history.\n- [JOpt Simple在新窗口打开](https://pholser.github.io/jopt-simple) - Fluent parser that uses the POSIX#getopt and GNU#getopt_long syntaxes.\n- [picocli在新窗口打开](http://picocli.info) - ANSI colors and styles in usage help with annotation-based POSIX/GNU/any syntax, subcommands, strong typing for both options and positional args.\n- [Text-IO在新窗口打开](https://github.com/beryx/text-io) - Aids the creation of full console-based applications.\n- [Lanterna在新窗口打开](https://github.com/mabe02/lanterna) - Easy console text-GUI library, similar to curses.\n\n## Cluster Management\n\n*Frameworks that can dynamically manage applications inside of a cluster.*\n\n- [Apache Aurora在新窗口打开](https://aurora.apache.org) - Mesos framework for long-running services and cron jobs.\n- [Apache Mesos在新窗口打开](https://mesos.apache.org) - Abstracts CPU, memory, storage, and other compute resources away from machines.\n- [Singularity在新窗口打开](http://getsingularity.com) - Mesos framework that makes deployment and operations easy. It supports web services, background workers, scheduled jobs, and one-off tasks.\n\n## Code Analysis\n\n*Tools that provide metrics and quality measurements.*\n\n- [Checkstyle在新窗口打开](https://github.com/checkstyle/checkstyle) - Static analysis of coding conventions and standards.\n- [Error Prone在新窗口打开](https://github.com/google/error-prone) - Catches common programming mistakes as compile-time errors.\n- [Infer在新窗口打开](https://github.com/facebook/infer) - Modern static analysis tool for verifying the correctness of code.\n- [jQAssistant在新窗口打开](https://jqassistant.org) - Static code analysis with Neo4J-based query language.\n- [NullAway在新窗口打开](https://github.com/uber/NullAway) - Eliminates NullPointerExceptions with low build-time overhead.\n- [PMD在新窗口打开](https://github.com/pmd/pmd) - Source code analysis for finding bad coding practices.\n- [SonarJava在新窗口打开](https://github.com/SonarSource/sonar-java) - Static analyzer for SonarQube & SonarLint.\n- [Sourcetrail ![c](https://cdn.rawgit.com/akullpp/23246ca832bda82bb505230bf3538e2a/raw/d9bcdb769bf025292f9c6bc1290f01f1fcd1f864/commercial.svg)在新窗口打开](https://www.sourcetrail.com) - Visual source code navigator.\n- [Spoon在新窗口打开](https://github.com/INRIA/spoon) - Library for analyzing and transforming Java source code.\n- [Spotbugs在新窗口打开](https://github.com/spotbugs/spotbugs) - Static analysis of bytecode to find potential bugs.\n\n## Code Coverage\n\n*Frameworks and tools that enable code coverage metrics collection for test suites.*\n\n- [Clover ![c](https://cdn.rawgit.com/akullpp/23246ca832bda82bb505230bf3538e2a/raw/d9bcdb769bf025292f9c6bc1290f01f1fcd1f864/commercial.svg)在新窗口打开](https://www.atlassian.com/software/clover/overview) - Relies on source-code instrumentation instead of bytecode instrumentation.\n- [Cobertura在新窗口打开](https://cobertura.github.io/cobertura) - Relies on offline (or static) bytecode instrumentation and class loading to collect code coverage metrics.\n- [JaCoCo在新窗口打开](http://eclemma.org/jacoco) - Framework that enables collection of code coverage metrics, using both offline and runtime bytecode instrumentation.\n\n## Code Generators\n\n*Tools that generate patterns for repetitive code in order to reduce verbosity and error-proneness.*\n\n- [ADT4J在新窗口打开](https://github.com/sviperll/adt4j) - JSR-269 code generator for algebraic data types.\n- [Auto在新窗口打开](https://github.com/google/auto) - Generates factory, service, and value classes.\n- [FreeBuilder在新窗口打开](https://github.com/google/FreeBuilder) - Automatically generates the Builder pattern.\n- [Immutables在新窗口打开](https://immutables.github.io) - Annotation processors to generate simple, safe and consistent value objects.\n- [JavaPoet在新窗口打开](https://github.com/square/javapoet) - API to generate source files.\n- [JHipster在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jhipster/generator-jhipster) - Yeoman source code generator for Spring Boot and AngularJS.\n- [Joda-Beans在新窗口打开](http://www.joda.org/joda-beans) - Small framework that adds queryable properties to Java, enhancing JavaBeans.\n- [Lombok在新窗口打开](https://projectlombok.org) - Code generator that aims to reduce verbosity.\n\n## Compiler-compiler\n\n*Frameworks that help to create parsers, interpreters or compilers.*\n\n- [ANTLR在新窗口打开](http://www.antlr.org) - Complex full-featured framework for top-down parsing.\n- [JavaCC在新窗口打开](https://javacc.org) - Parser generator that generates top-down parsers. Allows lexical state switching and permits extended BNF specifications.\n- [JFlex在新窗口打开](http://jflex.de) - A lexical analyzer generator.\n\n## Configuration\n\n*Libraries that provide external configuration.*\n\n- [centraldogma在新窗口打开](https://github.com/line/centraldogma) - Highly-available version-controlled service configuration repository based on Git, ZooKeeper and HTTP/2.\n- [cfg4j在新窗口打开](https://github.com/cfg4j/cfg4j) - Modern configuration library for distributed apps written in Java.\n- [config在新窗口打开](https://github.com/typesafehub/config) - Configuration library for JVM languages.\n- [dotenv在新窗口打开](https://github.com/shyiko/dotenv) - A twelve-factor configuration library for Java.\n- [ini4j在新窗口打开](http://ini4j.sourceforge.net) - Provides an API for handling Windows\' INI files.\n- [KAConf在新窗口打开](https://github.com/mariomac/kaconf) - Annotation-based configuration system for Java and Kotlin.\n- [owner在新窗口打开](https://github.com/lviggiano/owner) - Reduces boilerplate of properties.\n\n## Constraint Satisfaction Problem Solver\n\n*Libraries that help with implementing optimization and satisfiability problems.*\n\n- [Choco在新窗口打开](http://choco-solver.org) - Off-the-shelf constraint satisfaction problem solver that uses constraint programming techniques.\n- [JaCoP在新窗口打开](https://github.com/radsz/jacop) - Includes an interface for the FlatZinc language, enabling it to execute MiniZinc models.\n- [OptaPlanner在新窗口打开](https://www.optaplanner.org) - Business planning and resource scheduling optimization solver.\n\n## CSV\n\n*Frameworks and libraries that simplify reading/writing CSV data.*\n\n- [jackson-dataformat-csv在新窗口打开](https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson-dataformat-csv) - Jackson extension for reading and writing CSV.\n- [opencsv在新窗口打开](http://opencsv.sourceforge.net) - Simple CSV parser.\n- [Super CSV在新窗口打开](https://super-csv.github.io/super-csv) - Powerful CSV parser with support for Dozer, Joda-Time and Java 8.\n- [uniVocity-parsers在新窗口打开](https://github.com/uniVocity/univocity-parsers) - One of the fastest and most feature-complete parsers. Also comes with parsers for TSV and fixed-width records.\n\n## Database\n\n*Everything that simplifies interactions with the database.*\n\n- [Apache Phoenix在新窗口打开](https://phoenix.apache.org) - High-performance relational database layer over HBase for low-latency applications.\n- [Chronicle Map在新窗口打开](https://github.com/OpenHFT/Chronicle-Map) - Efficient, in-memory (opt. persisted to disk), off-heap key-value store.\n- [druid在新窗口打开](http://druid.io) - High-performance, column-oriented, distributed data store.\n- [eXist在新窗口打开](https://github.com/eXist-db/exist) - A NoSQL document database and application platform.\n- [FlexyPool在新窗口打开](https://github.com/vladmihalcea/flexy-pool) - Brings metrics and failover strategies to the most common connection pooling solutions.\n- [Flyway在新窗口打开](https://flywaydb.org) - Simple database migration tool.\n- [H2在新窗口打开](https://h2database.com) - Small SQL database notable for its in-memory functionality.\n- [HikariCP在新窗口打开](https://github.com/brettwooldridge/HikariCP) - High-performance JDBC connection pool.\n- [jasync-sql在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jasync-sql/jasync-sql) - Async DB driver for MySQL and PostgreSQL.\n- [JDBI在新窗口打开](http://jdbi.org) - Convenient abstraction of JDBC.\n- [Jedis在新窗口打开](https://github.com/xetorthio/jedis) - Small client for interaction with Redis, with methods for commands.\n- [Jest在新窗口打开](https://github.com/searchbox-io/Jest) - Client for the Elasticsearch REST API.\n- [jetcd在新窗口打开](https://github.com/justinsb/jetcd) - Client library for etcd.\n- [Jinq在新窗口打开](https://github.com/my2iu/Jinq) - Typesafe database queries via symbolic execution of Java 8 Lambdas (on top of JPA or jOOQ).\n- [jOOQ在新窗口打开](https://www.jooq.org) - Generates typesafe code based on SQL schema.\n- [Liquibase在新窗口打开](http://www.liquibase.org) - Database-independent library for tracking, managing and applying database schema changes.\n- [MapDB在新窗口打开](http://www.mapdb.org) - Embedded database engine that provides concurrent collections backed on disk or in off-heap memory.\n- [MariaDB4j在新窗口打开](https://github.com/vorburger/MariaDB4j) - Launcher for MariaDB that requires no installation or external dependencies.\n- [OrientDB在新窗口打开](https://orientdb.com/orientdb) - Embeddable distributed database written on top of Hazelcast.\n- [Presto在新窗口打开](https://github.com/prestodb/presto) - Distributed SQL query engine for big data.\